      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-01-31/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Happy Data Privacy Day! A Few Tips from the MVA Privacy and Data Security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JD Supra (press release) &amp;hellip; not required by law, more businesses are requiring these from their vendors, due to customer concerns arising from well-publicized data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.jdsupra.com/legalnews/happy-data-privacy-day-a-few-tips-from-61404/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.jdsupra.com/legalnews/happy-data-privacy-day-a-few-tips-from-61404/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Breaches and The Great Security Disconnect&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twitter; Facebook; LinkedIn; Credit Eligible. Data Breaches and The &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cuinfosecurity.com/whitepapers/data-breaches-great-security-disconnect-w-3056&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cuinfosecurity.com/whitepapers/data-breaches-great-security-disconnect-w-3056&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Executive Viewpoint 2017 Predictions: Thales e-Security  Facing the Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Virtual-Strategy Magazine Most people will agree that 2016 has been quite the year for cybersecurity. For starters, we saw not just one, but two major data breaches at Yahoo, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://virtual-strategy.com/2017/01/30/executive-viewpoint-2017-predictions-thales-e-security-facing-the-data-security-challenges-of-tomorrow/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://virtual-strategy.com/2017/01/30/executive-viewpoint-2017-predictions-thales-e-security-facing-the-data-security-challenges-of-tomorrow/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;ITRC-CyberScout Report: Govt-Military Sector Accounts for 7% of US Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ExecutiveBiz (blog) A new report by CyberScout and the Identity Theft Resource Center says the government and military sector represented 6.6 percent of the total &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2017/01/itrc-cyberscout-report-govt-military-sector-accounts-for-7-of-us-data-breaches-in-2016/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2017/01/itrc-cyberscout-report-govt-military-sector-accounts-for-7-of-us-data-breaches-in-2016/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Log Management: Configure, Troubleshoot, and Analyze&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;framework of choice for critical production .NET apps. Discover how to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bitpipe.com/detail/RES/1483978118_89.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bitpipe.com/detail/RES/1483978118_89.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;45% of NHS trusts scan for app vulnerabilities just once a year&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The NHS was one of the worst performing sectors in terms of the number of data breaches reported to the ICO last year. NHS contributed to 64 percent &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/45-of-nhs-trusts-scan-for-app-vulnerabilities-just-once-a-year/article/634702/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/45-of-nhs-trusts-scan-for-app-vulnerabilities-just-once-a-year/article/634702/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How to Protect Yourself From Soaring Data Breach Crimes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Goddijn says businesses were the targets of more than half (55 percent) of the data breaches in 2016, although government agencies and medical &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/protect-yourself-soaring-data-breach-075934458.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/protect-yourself-soaring-data-breach-075934458.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Protection Day: it&amp;rsquo;s important&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the increasing scale of data breaches and hacks we&amp;rsquo;ve seen recently, Data Protection Day has become more important than ever. Just this week &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-age.com/data-protection-day-important-123464196/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-age.com/data-protection-day-important-123464196/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Encryption and Reformatting Drives Might Seem Convenient &amp;amp; Reliable, But&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance 31, 2017 /PRNewswire/ &amp;ndash; In recent years, a growing number of data breaches have resulted from the improper data removal and insecure storage of &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/encryption-reformatting-drives-might-seem-110000198.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/encryption-reformatting-drives-might-seem-110000198.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Why the EU data protection is a game changer for hoteliers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the GDPR on the horizon, and stricter penalties for serious data breaches, there is added impetus for hoteliers to bolster data security processes.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/why-the-eu-data-protection-is-a-game-changer-for-hoteliers/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/why-the-eu-data-protection-is-a-game-changer-for-hoteliers/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Varonis Keeps Client Data at Utah&amp;rsquo;s Largest Law Firm Secure from&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance Varonis solutions monitor file activity and user behavior, prevent data breaches from the inside out, and make permissions management and auditing &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/varonis-keeps-client-data-utah-130000873.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/varonis-keeps-client-data-utah-130000873.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Industrial Cybersecurity Industry Leader, Eric Byres, Joins Verve&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance &amp;hellip; platform that consolidates antivirus, application whitelisting, change &amp;amp; configuration management, security information &amp;amp; event management (SIEM), &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/industrial-cybersecurity-industry-leader-eric-134000633.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/industrial-cybersecurity-industry-leader-eric-134000633.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breach costs exceed 20% of revenue&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The cost of data breaches amounted to more than 20% of revenue, on top of substantial loss of customers and opportunities, for more than a third of &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450412041/Data-breach-costs-exceed-20-of-revenue&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450412041/Data-breach-costs-exceed-20-of-revenue&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Imperial researcher talks about improving security around healthcare data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A report that came out in the USA late last year found that the US healthcare industry suffered an estimated of $6.2 Billion in data breaches per year.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www3.imperial.ac.uk/portal/page/portallive/4767547BE586E931E050C69B473972F1&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www3.imperial.ac.uk/portal/page/portallive/4767547BE586E931E050C69B473972F1&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Comodo extends endpoint protection to Mac and Linux&lt;/h3&gt;
